## Regular Expressions & Skip Expressions

Below are community suggested expressions

<<<<<<< HEAD
### Starr Apps

#### Radarr

##### Radarr Regular Expression

```regex
(?i)(\|warn\||\|error\||^\[v4.+\])
```

##### Radarr Skip Expression

```regex
(?i)Movie with IMDBId|It will not be added|Invalid date found|Validation failed|An unhandled exception has occurred while executing the request.
```

#### Sonarr

##### Sonarr Regular Expression

```regex
(?i)(\|warn\||\|error\||^\[v(?:v(?:3|4).+\])
```

##### Sonarr Skip Expression

```regex
(?i)Invalid date found|Validation failed|An unhandled exception has occurred while executing the request.|Unable to find exact quality
```

#### Prowlarr

##### Prowlarr Regular Expression

```regex
(?i)(\|warn\||\|error\||^\[v0.+\])
```

##### Prowlarr Skip Expression

```regex
(?i)Validation failed|An unhandled exception has occurred while executing the request|(?:CinemaZ|PrivateHD)[.a-z0-9/=&?: ]+404\.NotFound
```

#### Readarr

##### Readarr Regular Expression

```regex
(?i)(\|warn\||\|error\||^\[v0.+\])
```

##### Readarr Skip Expression

```regex
(?i)Validation failed|An unhandled exception has occurred while executing the request.
```

#### Lidarr

##### Lidarr Regular Expression

```regex
(?i)(\|warn\||\|error\||^\[v1.+\])
```

##### Lidarr Skip Expression

```regex
(?i)Validation failed|An unhandled exception has occurred while executing the request.
```
